item.description:
I have been craving Mexican food, and made this reservation for the group. Good reviews of this place are "small chain withvery good home style mexican cooking". This is the MANSFIELD restaurant (not Hartford). Their website is http://www.mycoyotefl...

I know this is short notice, but hope to see you there. Please only RSVP "YES" if you will definitely be there. I will collect $1.00 each to defray costs of running this meetup. I will confirm the reservation Tuesday noon for the deck if the weather looks good.

- Betsy

group.name: The Ethnic Dining Enthusiasts Meetup Group
